When we first found Kiva we were very impressed at the professionalism and the human outreach that is behind the program and we fully endorse what Kiva stands for.

We loan because we believe that the easiest way to help someone is to give them the means to help themselves.  Kiva provides a way to do this.
lenders.occupational_info: We provide the world wide community of pagans and other nature-based religions of the world a way to bring together the knowledge and experiences of the entire community. We do this through our online community, our various outreach programs and by being available for research and writings by prominent figures within the world wide pagan community.
